{
  "stem": "3804.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he said-- we gave him some numbers, and he helped it, you know, somehow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "No, no, this is number this and this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In the end of the 20 minutes, he said, ich bin Adolf Eichmann, I am Adolf Eichmann.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we dressed him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We put him on a-- everything was ready, the room.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Were not too many things there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One bedroom, that he was chained-- chained to his leg.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Only we didn't need so much the chain, but OK.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All the other operators would be in the other side of this villa.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] was, I put him in the bed, and he was laying there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[COUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I had a high chair there to watch him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Naomi was the veranda there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- a friend of mine was there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The uzi was sitting there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The other people with the woman was the kitchen nearby-- had the kitchen and the room that I slept nearby, sometimes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the woman that I slept with her together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Was only one bed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] We slept there, because I have to be near to him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But most of the time-- most of the time, I was with him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had this small book, the red, small book that I was reading, the diary of South America, how you come to South America-- this small, red book.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I, most of the time, was painting, you know, and the diary, because I had disguise, and all this makeup, this kind of [INAUDIBLE] disguising him, was also painting in this book.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it came out that, later, I painted about 60 small paintings during my time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I didn't know even--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the pages of the book.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the pages of the book, both sides.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't know I never will use it, or not.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
